{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775844990799,"sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","part":{"id":"prt_d789c1858001IQxS4m1APrQVtZ","messageID":"msg_d789bfd74001VHbx3AVGcOXzMc","sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-de67b4d71bc846dd88a7c24d9430e117","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n8: \n9: ### Time threshold\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n13: ```\n14: \n15: Idle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n16: \n17: ### Annotation key\n18: \n19: The reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n20: \n21: - Import: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n22: - Key: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` = **`\"last-activity-time\"`**\n23: \n24: (Workload manager also sets `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` on Sandbox metadata for template-driven idle configuration; **agentd** only reads `last-activity-time`.)\n25: \n26: ### Reconciler\n27: \n28: ```go\n29: package agentd\n30: \n31: type Reconciler struct {\n32:     client.Client\n33:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n34: }\n35: \n36: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\n37: ```\n38: \n39: **Algorithm (exact behavior):**\n40: \n41: 1. `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`.\n42: 2. If `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`.\n43: 3. If other get error → return `ctrl.Result{}, err`.\n44: 4. `lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`.\n45: 5. If `exists && lastActivityStr != \"\"`:\n46:    - `lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`\n47:    - If parse err → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err`\n48:    - `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n49:    - If `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`:\n50:      - `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`; if err and not `IsNotFound` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n51:    - Else:\n52:      - `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n53: 6. `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n54: \n55: ### SetupWithManager\n56: \n57: ```go\n58: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n59:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n60:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n61:         Complete(r)\n62: }\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ## Binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n66: \n67: ### Scheme registration\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n71: \n72: func init() {\n73:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n74:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n75: }\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ### Controller-runtime manager\n79: \n80: ```go\n81: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n82:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n83:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n84:     HealthProbeBindAddress:   \"0\",\n85: })\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### Controller registration (duplicate of SetupWithManager pattern)\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n92:     For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n93:     Complete(&agentd.Reconciler{\n94:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n95:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n96:     })\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ### Run\n100: \n101: ```go\n102: mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())\n103: ```\n104: \n105: ## Watched resources\n106: \n107: | API group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n108: |-----------|---------|------|---------|\n109: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Default `For()` watch — creates, updates, deletes (per controller-runtime) |\n110: \n111: No explicit `Owns` or `Watches` — single primary resource `Sandbox`.\n112: \n113: ## Related workload-manager constants (context)\n114: \n115: From `pkg/workloadmanager` (not used by agentd reconcile logic but set when sandboxes are created):\n116: \n117: - `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"` — duration string on Sandbox CR.\n118: - `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` — **read by agentd** for idle cleanup.\n119: \n120: ## Dependencies\n121: \n122: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n123: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n124: - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`\n125: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`\n126: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` (annotation key only)\n\n(End of file - total 126 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n\n### Time threshold\n\n```go\nvar SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n```\n\nIdle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n\n### Annotation key\n\nThe reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/design.md","time":{"start":1775844990782,"end":1775844990798}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775844990802,"sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","part":{"id":"prt_d789c1b4f001RcLS3RLfjix0ph","messageID":"msg_d789bfd74001VHbx3AVGcOXzMc","sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-acde755f956a497fa70e87f44358b586","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Sandbox Orchestration — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module and dependencies\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|--------|\n7: | Go module | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n8: | Go version (go.mod) | `1.24.4` |\n9: | Toolchain | `go1.24.9` |\n10: \n11: **Direct `require` (from go.mod):**  \n12: `github.com/agiledragon/gomonkey/v2 v2.13.0`, `github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.35.0`, `github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0`, `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.2`, `github.com/google/uuid v1.6.0`, `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.17.1`, `github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1`, `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go v1.0.69`, `golang.org/x/net v0.47.0`, `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1`, `k8s.io/utils v0.0.0-20251002143259-bc988d571ff4`, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox v0.1.1`, `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`\n13: \n14: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n15: \n16: ### groupversion_info.go — package and scheme\n17: \n18: ```go\n19: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n20: package v1alpha1\n21: \n22: var (\n23:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n24:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n25:     AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n26: )\n27: ```\n28: \n29: ### register.go — kind metadata\n30: \n31: ```go\n32: var (\n33:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n34:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n35:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n36:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n37: )\n38: \n39: var (\n40:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n41:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n42:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n43: )\n44: \n45: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n46: \n47: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n48:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n49: }\n50: ```\n51: \n52: ### agent_type.go — AgentRuntime types\n53: \n54: ```go\n55: // +genclient\n56: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n57: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n58: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n59: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n60: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n61: type AgentRuntime struct {\n62:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n63:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n64:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n65:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n66: }\n67: \n68: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n69:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n70:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n71:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n72:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n73:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n74:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n75:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n76:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n77:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n78: }\n79: \n80: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n81:     // +optional\n82:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n83: }\n84: \n85: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n86:     // +optional\n87:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n88:     // +optional\n89:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n90:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n91:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n92: }\n93: \n94: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n95: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n96: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n97:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n98:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n99:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n100: }\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ### codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter and shared types\n104: \n105: ```go\n106: // +genclient\n107: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n108: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n109: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n110: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n111: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n112: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n113:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n114:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n115:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n116:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n117: }\n118: \n119: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n122:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n123:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n124:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n125:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n126:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n127:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n128:     // +optional\n129:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n130:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n131:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n132:     // +optional\n133:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n134: }\n135: \n136: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n137:     // +optional\n138:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n139:     // +optional\n140:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n141: }\n142: \n143: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n144:     // +optional\n145:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n146:     // +optional\n147:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n148:     // +optional\n149:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n150:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n151:     // +optional\n152:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n153:     // +optional\n154:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n155:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n156:     // +listType=map\n157:     // +listMapKey=name\n158:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n159:     // +optional\n160:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n161:     // +optional\n162:     // +listType=atomic\n163:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n164:     // +optional\n165:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n166:     // +optional\n167:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n168: }\n169: \n170: type TargetPort struct {\n171:     // +optional\n172:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n173:     // +optional\n174:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n175:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n176:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n177:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n178:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n179: }\n180: \n181: type AuthModeType string\n182: \n183: const (\n184:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n185:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n186: )\n187: \n188: type ProtocolType string\n189: \n190: const (\n191:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n192:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n193: )\n194: \n195: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n196: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n197: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n198:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n199:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n200:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n201: }\n202: ```\n203: \n204: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`\n205: \n206: ```go\n207: const (\n208:     AgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n209:     CodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n210:     SandboxKind         = \"Sandbox\"\n211:     SandboxClaimsKind   = \"SandboxClaim\"\n212: )\n213: \n214: type SandboxInfo struct {\n215:     Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n216:     SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n217:     SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n218:     Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n219:     EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n220:     SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n221:     CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n222:     ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n223:     Status string `json:\"status\"`\n224: }\n225: \n226: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n227:     Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n228:     Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n229:     Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n230: }\n231: \n232: type CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n233:     Kind      string `json:\"kind\"`\n234:     Name      string `json:\"name\"`\n235:     Namespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n236: }\n237: \n238: type CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n239:     SessionID   string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n240:     SandboxID   string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n241:     SandboxName string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n242:     EntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n243: }\n244: \n245: func (car *CreateSandboxRequest) Validate() error\n246: ```\n247: \n248: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/api`\n249: \n250: ```go\n251: const (\n252:     resourceGroup               = \"agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n253:     sessionResourceName         = \"sessions\"\n254:     agentRuntimeResourceName    = \"agentruntimes\"\n255:     codeInterpreterResourceName = \"codeinterpreters\"\n256: )\n257: \n258: var (\n259:     ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound    = errors.New(\"agent runtime not found\")\n260:     ErrCodeInterpreterNotFound = errors.New(\"code interpreter not found\")\n261:     ErrTemplateMissing         = errors.New(\"resource has no pod template\")\n262:     ErrPublicKeyMissing        = errors.New(\"public key not yet loaded from Router Secret\")\n263: )\n264: \n265: func NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID string) error\n266: func NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(namespace, name, kind string) error\n267: func NewUpstreamUnavailableError(err error) error\n268: func NewInternalError(err error) error\n269: ```\n270: \n271: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n272: \n273: ### Config and Server\n274: \n275: ```go\n276: type Config struct {\n277:     Port             string\n278:     RuntimeClassName string\n279:     EnableTLS        bool\n280:     TLSCert          string\n281:     TLSKey           string\n282:     EnableAuth       bool\n283: }\n284: \n285: type Server struct {\n286:     config            *Config\n287:     router            *gin.Engine\n288:     httpServer        *http.Server\n289:     k8sClient         *K8sClient\n290:     sandboxController *SandboxReconciler\n291:     tokenCache        *TokenCache\n292:     informers         *Informers\n293:     storeClient       store.Store\n294:     wg                sync.WaitGroup\n295: }\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ### HTTP routes\n299: \n300: | Method | Path | Auth middleware | Handler |\n301: |--------|------|-----------------|---------|\n302: | GET | `/health` | No | `handleHealth` |\n303: | POST | `/v1/agent-runtime` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleAgentRuntimeCreate` |\n304: | DELETE | `/v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleDeleteSandbox` |\n305: | POST | `/v1/code-interpreter` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleCodeInterpreterCreate` |\n306: | DELETE | `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleDeleteSandbox` |\n307: \n308: ### ErrorResponse\n309: \n310: ```go\n311: type ErrorResponse struct {\n312:     Message string `json:\"message\"`\n313: }\n314: ```\n315: \n316: ### K8sClient and defaults\n317: \n318: ```go\n319: const (\n320:     DefaultSandboxTTL         = 8 * time.Hour\n321:     DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n322: )\n323: \n324: var (\n325:     SessionIdLabelKey         = \"runtime.agentcube.io/session-id\"\n326:     WorkloadNameLabelKey      = \"runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name\"\n327:     SandboxNameLabelKey       = \"runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name\"\n328:     LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n329:     IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey  = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\n330: )\n331: \n332: type K8sClient struct {\n333:     clientset       *kubernetes.Clientset\n334:     dynamicClient   dynamic.Interface\n335:     scheme          *runtime.Scheme\n336:     baseConfig      *rest.Config\n337:     clientCache     *ClientCache\n338:     dynamicInformer dynamicinformer.DynamicSharedInformerFactory\n339:     informerFactory informers.SharedInformerFactory\n340:     podInformer     cache.SharedIndexInformer\n341:     podLister       listersv1.PodLister\n342: }\n343: ```\n344: \n345: - REST config: `QPS = 50`, `Burst = 100`; in-cluster config else kubeconfig loading rules.\n346: - `NewClientCache(100)` for user dynamic clients.\n347: \n348: ### GVR variables (`informers.go`)\n349: \n350: ```go\n351: var (\n352:     AgentRuntimeGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n353:         Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\",\n354:     }\n355:     CodeInterpreterGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n356:         Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"codeinterpreters\",\n357:     }\n358:     SandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n359:         Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"sandboxes\",\n360:     }\n361:     SandboxClaimGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n362:         Group: \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n363:     }\n364: )\n365: ```\n366: \n367: ### Identity secret (workload_builder.go)\n368: \n369: ```go\n370: const (\n371:     IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n372:     PublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n373: )\n374: \n375: var IdentitySecretNamespace = \"default\" // overridden by env AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE if set\n376: ```\n377: \n378: ### Sandbox reconciler\n379: \n380: ```go\n381: type SandboxReconciler struct {\n382:     client.Client\n383:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n384:     watchers map[types.NamespacedName]chan SandboxStatusUpdate\n385:     mu       sync.RWMutex\n386: }\n387: \n388: type SandboxStatusUpdate struct {\n389:     Sandbox *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox\n390: }\n391: ```\n392: \n393: - `Reconcile`: when `getSandboxStatus(sandbox) == \"running\"`, notify waiter channel (buffer 1), non-blocking send with `default` branch warning on full channel.\n394: - `getSandboxStatus`: returns `\"running\"` if a condition has `Type == string(sandboxv1alpha1.SandboxConditionReady)` and `Status == metav1.ConditionTrue`, else `\"unknown\"`.\n395: \n396: ### Garbage collector\n397: \n398: ```go\n399: const gcOnceTimeout = 2 * time.Minute\n400: \n401: type garbageCollector struct {\n402:     k8sClient   *K8sClient\n403:     interval    time.Duration\n404:     storeClient store.Store\n405: }\n406: ```\n407: \n408: - `newGarbageCollector(k8s, store, 15*time.Second)` — **GC interval: 15s**.\n409: - Per tick: `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, time.Now().Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout), 16)` — **batch size 16**.\n410: - `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Now(), 16)` — **batch size 16**.\n411: - Single tick context timeout: **2 minutes**.\n412: \n413: ### Token cache\n414: \n415: - `NewTokenCache(1000, 5*time.Minute)` — max entries **1000**, TTL **5m** per entry (LRU + last-access expiry).\n416: \n417: ### Auth context keys\n418: \n419: ```go\n420: type contextKey string\n421: \n422: const (\n423:     contextKeyUserToken          contextKey = \"userToken\"\n424:     contextKeyServiceAccount     contextKey = \"serviceAccount\"\n425:     contextKeyServiceAccountName contextKey = \"serviceAccountName\"\n426:     contextKeyNamespace          contextKey = \"namespace\"\n427: )\n428: ```\n429: \n430: ### CLI flags (`cmd/workload-manager/main.go`)\n431: \n432: | Flag | Default | Meaning |\n433: |------|---------|---------|\n434: | `-port` | `8080` | API port |\n435: | `-runtime-class-name` | `kuasar-vmm` | Stored on `Config.RuntimeClassName` (flag parsed in `main`; **not read** elsewhere in `pkg/workloadmanager` in current source) |\n436: | `-enable-tls` | `false` | TLS |\n437: | `-tls-cert` | `\"\"` | Cert path |\n438: | `-tls-key` | `\"\"` | Key path |\n439: | `-enable-auth` | `false` | TokenReview auth |\n440: \n441: - Controller-runtime manager: metrics bind `0`, health probe `0`.\n442: - Shutdown: HTTP shutdown timeout **15s**, then cancel ctx, `WaitForBackgroundWorkers`, `CloseStore`.\n443: \n444: ### Store dependency\n445: \n446: ```go\n447: // github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store\n448: type Store interface {\n449:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n450:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n451:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n452:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n453:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n454:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n455:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n456:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n457:     Close() error\n458: }\n459: ```\n460: \n461: Server uses `store.Storage()` singleton.\n462: \n463: ### Sandbox build notes\n464: \n465: - AgentRuntime: sandbox name `{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`, UUID session ID, ports from `spec.Ports`, TTL/idle from `MaxSessionDuration` / `SessionTimeout` when non-nil.\n466: - CodeInterpreter: default ports if empty: single `TargetPort{Port:8080, Protocol:ProtocolTypeHTTP, PathPrefix:\"/\"}`; if `WarmPoolSize > 0`: creates `SandboxClaim` + minimal `Sandbox` metadata only, `sandboxEntry.Kind = SandboxClaimsKind`; else builds full `Sandbox` with container `code-interpreter` and optional `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` when `AuthMode == picod`.\n467: - `buildSandboxObject`: APIVersion `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, Kind `Sandbox`, labels include `managed-by: agentcube-workload-manager`, annotation `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey` = idle duration string, lifecycle `ShutdownTime` = now+TTL, `Replicas: ptr.To[int32](1)`.\n468: \n469: ### Pod name annotation\n470: \n471: - Read from created sandbox: key from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/controllers`.`SandboxPodNameAnnotation` (comment in source documents value `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name`).\n472: \n473: ## CodeInterpreter controller (supplementary)\n474: \n475: - Reconciles `CodeInterpreter`; when `WarmPoolSize > 0` ensures `SandboxTemplate` (name = CI name) and `SandboxWarmPool` (name = CI name, replicas = WarmPoolSize, templateRef name = CI name); injects `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` in template unless `AuthModeNone`; requeues 5s if public key not cached and auth not none.\n\n(End of file - total 475 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Sandbox Orchestration — Design\n\n## Module and dependencies\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|--------|\n| Go module | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Go version (go.mod) | `1.24.4` |\n| Toolchain | `go1.24.9` |\n\n**Direct `require` (from go.mod):**  \n`github.com/agiledragon/gomonkey/v2 v2.13.0`, `github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.35.0`, `github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0`, `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.2`, `github.com/google/uuid v1.6.0`, `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.17.1`, `github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1`, `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go v1.0.69`, `golang.org/x/net v0.47.0`, `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1`, `k8s.io/utils v0.0.0-20251002143259-bc988d571ff4`, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox v0.1.1`, `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n\n### groupversion_info.go — package and scheme\n\n```go\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md","time":{"start":1775844990785,"end":1775844990800}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775844990818,"sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","part":{"id":"prt_d789c1f2b001WoqVhFK62Ofbje","messageID":"msg_d789bfd74001VHbx3AVGcOXzMc","sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-e64e16ee9a83461b91c1e073f9aa18e5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n22: - 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n23: - Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理运行时实例\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | PodSpec、EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements 等 |\n30: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n31: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n32: \n33: ### Controller-gen Markers\n34: \n35: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n36: |--------|------------|---------|\n37: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n38: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n39: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n40: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n41: | `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n42: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n43: \n44: ## Data Structures\n45: \n46: ### groupversion_info.go\n47: \n48: ```go\n49: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n50: package v1alpha1\n51: \n52: import \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n53: \n54: var (\n55:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n56:         Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n57:         Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n58:     }\n59:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n60:     AddToScheme   = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n61: )\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ### register.go\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: var (\n68:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n69:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n70:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n71:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n72: \n73:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n74:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n75:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n76: )\n77: \n78: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n79: \n80: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n81:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n82: }\n83: ```\n84: \n85: ### AgentRuntime Types\n86: \n87: ```go\n88: // +genclient\n89: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n90: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n91: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n92: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n93: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n94: type AgentRuntime struct {\n95:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n96:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n97:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n98:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n99: }\n100: \n101: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n102:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n103:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n104:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n105:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n106:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n107:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n108:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n109:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n110:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n111:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n112: }\n113: \n114: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n115:     // +optional\n116:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n117: }\n118: \n119: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n122:     // +optional\n123:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n124:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n125:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n126: }\n127: \n128: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n129: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n130: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n131:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n132:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n133:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n134: }\n135: ```\n136: \n137: ### CodeInterpreter Types\n138: \n139: ```go\n140: // +genclient\n141: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n142: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n143: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n144: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n145: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n146: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n147:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n148:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n149:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n150:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n151: }\n152: \n153: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n154:     // +optional\n155:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n156:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n157:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n158:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n159:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n160:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n161:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n162:     // +optional\n163:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n164:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n165:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n166:     // +optional\n167:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n168: }\n169: \n170: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n171:     // +optional\n172:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n173:     // +optional\n174:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n175: }\n176: \n177: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n178:     // +optional\n179:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n180:     // +optional\n181:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n182:     // +optional\n183:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n184:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n185:     // +optional\n186:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n187:     // +optional\n188:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n189:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n190:     // +listType=map\n191:     // +listMapKey=name\n192:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n193:     // +optional\n194:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n195:     // +optional\n196:     // +listType=atomic\n197:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n198:     // +optional\n199:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n200:     // +optional\n201:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n202: }\n203: \n204: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n205: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n206: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n207:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n208:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n209:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n210: }\n211: ```\n212: \n213: ### Shared Types\n214: \n215: ```go\n216: type TargetPort struct {\n217:     // +optional\n218:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n219:     // +optional\n220:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n221:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n222:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n223:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n224:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n225: }\n226: \n227: type AuthModeType string\n228: \n229: const (\n230:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n231:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n232: )\n233: \n234: type ProtocolType string\n235: \n236: const (\n237:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n238:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n239: )\n240: ```\n241: \n242: ## API Schema\n243: \n244: ### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n245: \n246: | Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n247: |----------|----------------------|\n248: | AgentRuntime | `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration` |\n249: | CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n250: \n251: ### Defaults\n252: \n253: | Field | Default Value |\n254: |-------|---------------|\n255: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n256: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n257: | `authMode` | `picod` |\n258: | `targetPort[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n259: \n260: ### Enums\n261: \n262: | Field | Allowed Values |\n263: |-------|----------------|\n264: | `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n265: | `protocol` | `HTTP`, `HTTPS` |\n266: \n267: ### REST Resource Plurals\n268: \n269: | Kind | Plural |\n270: |------|--------|\n271: | AgentRuntime | `agentruntimes` |\n272: | CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n273: \n274: ### Printer Columns\n275: \n276: | Name | Type | JSONPath |\n277: |------|------|----------|\n278: | Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n279: \n280: ## Error Handling\n281: \n282: - 无 spec 必填字段时，API server 拒绝创建请求（validation error）\n283: - 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n284: - Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n285: \n286: ## Testing Strategy\n287: \n288: ### Unit Tests\n289: \n290: | Test Category | Coverage |\n291: |---------------|----------|\n292: | DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段（deep vs shallow） |\n293: | Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n294: | Enum validation | 测试所有允许值及无效值 |\n295: | JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n296: \n297: ### Integration Tests\n298: \n299: - CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n300: - Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n301: \n302: ### Test File Structure\n303: \n304: ```\n305: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n306:   types_test.go       — DeepCopy、默认值、JSON 序列化测试\n307: ```\n308: \n309: ### Test Utilities\n310: \n311: 使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/webhook` 进行 validation 测试（如需 webhook）。\n312: \n313: ## File Structure\n314: \n315: ```\n316: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n317:   groupversion_info.go   — GroupVersion 定义、SchemeBuilder\n318:   register.go            — Kind constants、Resource helper\n319:   agentruntime_types.go  — AgentRuntime、AgentRuntimeList、SandboxTemplate\n320:   codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、共享类型\n321:   doc.go                 — 包文档（可选）\n322: \n323: client-go/                — 由 make gen-client 生成\n324:   clientset/\n325:   informers/\n326:   listers/\n327: ```\n328: \n329: ## Generation Commands\n330: \n331: | Command | Output |\n332: |---------|--------|\n333: | `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML（`manifests/charts/base/crds/`） |\n334: | `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n335: | `make gen-all` | 以上全部 |\n336: \n337: ## Open Questions\n338: \n339: - [已解决] 默认值由 kubebuilder markers 定义\n340: - [已解决] Status 字段包含 `Conditions`（通用）和 `Ready`（CodeInterpreter）\n341: - 是否需要添加 additionalPrinterColumns（如 Ready 状态）？\n342: - 是否需要 webhook 进行更复杂验证？\n343: \n344: ## References\n345: \n346: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n347: - client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n348: - controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`\n\n(End of file - total 348 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nCRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775844990787,"end":1775844990814}}}}
