{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845080622,"sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","part":{"id":"prt_d789d7dc6001YdcsDmR8Nver6d","messageID":"msg_d789c1f9d001CJrA6LNmxuXtVb","sessionID":"ses_28764ab3fffegPoGoQWmGYHLx2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-583c521ca4e947df93fdea58493b5e6e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-006/design.md","content":"# AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n实现 Sandbox 删除处理器及生命周期管理机制，包括：\n- 删除 Sandbox CR 及关联资源（Pod、ServiceAccount 等）\n- TTL 过期清理、Idle timeout 检测、Max session duration 限制\n- Garbage Collector 定期清理失效 Sandbox\n- 与 agentd 的 idle cleanup 协调\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── lifecycle.go              — Sandbox 生命周期管理核心逻辑\n├── lifecycle_test.go         — 生命周期测试\n├── garbage_collector.go      — GC 定期清理器\n├── garbage_collector_test.go — GC 测试\n├── deletion_handler.go       — DELETE /v1/{kind}/sessions/:sessionId 处理器\n├── deletion_handler_test.go  — 删除处理器测试\n├── k8s_client.go             — (existing) K8sClient 扩展删除方法\n├── types.go                  — (existing) Store interface、错误类型\n├── defaults.go               — (existing) TTL/Timeout 常量\n└── handlers/\n    └── sandbox_delete.go     — Sandbox 删除 HTTP handler\n```\n\n**组件交互图：**\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n│  HTTP DELETE    │────▶│  DeletionHandler │────▶│    K8sClient    │\n│  /sessions/:id  │     │                  │     │  (dynamic client)│\n└─────────────────┘     └──────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n                               │                        │\n                               ▼                        ▼\n                        ┌──────────────┐         ┌──────────────┐\n                        │    Store     │         │  Sandbox CR  │\n                        │ (Redis/Valkey│         │  + Pod SA    │\n                        └──────────────┘         └──────────────┘\n\n┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Garbage Collector (goroutine)              │\n│  ┌─────────────┐   ┌─────────────┐   ┌─────────────────────┐  │\n│  │ interval    │──▶│ ListExpired │──▶│ Delete Sandbox CR   │  │\n│  │ (2min tick) │   │ + Inactive  │   │ + cleanup Store     │  │\n│  └─────────────┘   └─────────────┘   └─────────────────────┘  │\n└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` | 判断 NotFound、Conflict 等 K8s 错误 |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | DeleteOptions、GracePeriodSeconds |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic` | Dynamic client 删除 Sandbox CR |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Sandbox 类型定义 |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` | SandboxInfo、Store interface |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | Typed client for AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | Labels/Annotations 常量 |\n\n### Integration with client-go\n\nclient-go library (`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`) 提供：\n\n```go\nimport (\n    agentcubeclient \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n    runtimev1alpha1 \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\ntype AgentCubeClient struct {\n    clientset agentcubeclient.Interface\n}\n\nfunc NewAgentCubeClient(config *rest.Config) (*AgentCubeClient, error) {\n    clientset, err := agentcubeclient.NewForConfig(config)\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to create agentcube clientset: %w\", err)\n    }\n    return &AgentCubeClient{clientset: clientset}, nil\n}\n\nfunc (c *AgentCubeClient) AgentRuntimes(namespace string) runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInterface {\n    return c.clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(namespace)\n}\n\nfunc (c *AgentCubeClient) CodeInterpreters(namespace string) runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInterface {\n    return c.clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().CodeInterpreters(namespace)\n}\n```\n\n用于查询 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 的 sessionTimeout/maxSessionDuration 配置。\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### DeleteSandboxRequest\n\n```go\ntype DeleteSandboxRequest struct {\n    SessionID string `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    Kind      string `json:\"kind\"` // \"agent-runtime\" or \"code-interpreter\"\n}\n```\n\n### DeleteSandboxResponse\n\n```go\ntype DeleteSandboxResponse struct {\n    SessionID string `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    Status    string `json:\"status\"` // \"deleted\" or \"deleting\"\n    Message   string `json:\"message,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n### LifecycleConfig\n\n```go\ntype LifecycleConfig struct {\n    DefaultTTL             time.Duration // 8h\n    DefaultIdleTimeout     time.Duration // 15m\n    DefaultMaxDuration     time.Duration // 8h\n    GCInterval             time.Duration // 2min\n    GCOnceTimeout          time.Duration // 2min\n    DeletionGracePeriod    int64         // 0 (immediate)\n    DeletionTimeout        time.Duration // 30s\n}\n```\n\n### SandboxLifecycleManager\n\n```go\ntype SandboxLifecycleManager struct {\n    k8sClient      *K8sClient\n    agentcubeClient *AgentCubeClient\n    store          Store\n    config         LifecycleConfig\n    logger         Logger\n}\n```\n\n### GarbageCollector\n\n```go\ntype GarbageCollector struct {\n    manager    *SandboxLifecycleManager\n    interval   time.Duration\n    onceTimeout time.Duration\n    stopCh     chan struct{}\n    wg         sync.WaitGroup\n}\n\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) Start()\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) Stop()\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) runOnce(ctx context.Context) error\n```\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n### DELETE `/v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId`\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Method | DELETE |\n| Path | `/v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` |\n| Auth | If `EnableAuth` |\n| Handler | `handleDeleteAgentRuntimeSandbox` |\n\n**Response (200):**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"sessionId\": \"abc-123\",\n  \"status\": \"deleted\"\n}\n```\n\n**Response (404):**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"NOT_FOUND\",\n  \"message\": \"session not found: abc-123\"\n}\n```\n\n### DELETE `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId`\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Method | DELETE |\n| Path | `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` |\n| Auth | If `EnableAuth` |\n| Handler | `handleDeleteCodeInterpreterSandbox` |\n\n**Response:** 同上\n\n## Lifecycle Management Logic\n\n### Delete Sandbox Flow\n\n```go\nfunc (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) DeleteSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error {\n    // 1. Get sandbox info from store\n    sandboxInfo, err := m.store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n    if err != nil {\n        if errors.Is(err, ErrSandboxNotFound) {\n            return &NotFoundError{Resource: \"session\", Name: sessionID}\n        }\n        return &InternalError{Err: err}\n    }\n\n    // 2. Delete Sandbox CR via dynamic client\n    sandboxGVR := schema.GroupVersionResource{\n        Group:    \"agents.x-k8s.io\",\n        Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n        Resource: \"sandboxes\",\n    }\n\n    deleteOpts := metav1.DeleteOptions{\n        GracePeriodSeconds: ptr.To[int64](m.config.DeletionGracePeriod),\n    }\n\n    err = m.k8sClient.DynamicClient().Resource(sandboxGVR).\n        Namespace(sandboxInfo.SandboxNamespace).\n        Delete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, deleteOpts)\n    \n    if err != nil && !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n        return &InternalError{Err: fmt.Errorf(\"delete sandbox CR: %w\", err)}\n    }\n\n    // 3. If SandboxClaim was used, delete it too\n    if sandboxInfo.Kind == types.SandboxClaimKind {\n        claimGVR := schema.GroupVersionResource{\n            Group:    \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\",\n            Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n            Resource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n        }\n        m.k8sClient.DynamicClient().Resource(claimGVR).\n            Namespace(sandboxInfo.SandboxNamespace).\n            Delete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, deleteOpts)\n    }\n\n    // 4. Delete from store\n    err = m.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n    if err != nil {\n        m.logger.Error(\"failed to delete from store\", \"sessionID\", sessionID, \"err\", err)\n    }\n\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n### TTL & Timeout Calculation\n\n```go\nfunc (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) CalculateLifecycle(\n    kind string,\n    namespace string,\n    name string,\n) (ttl, idleTimeout, maxDuration time.Duration, err error) {\n    \n    ttl = m.config.DefaultTTL\n    idleTimeout = m.config.DefaultIdleTimeout\n    maxDuration = m.config.DefaultMaxDuration\n\n    // Query AgentRuntime or CodeInterpreter for configured values\n    switch kind {\n    case types.AgentRuntimeKind:\n        ar, err := m.agentcubeClient.AgentRuntimes(namespace).Get(\n            ctx, name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n        if err != nil {\n            if apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n                return // use defaults\n            }\n            return ttl, idleTimeout, maxDuration, err\n        }\n        if ar.Spec.SessionTimeout != nil {\n            idleTimeout = ar.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration\n        }\n        if ar.Spec.MaxSessionDuration != nil {\n            maxDuration = ar.Spec.MaxSessionDuration.Duration\n        }\n        ttl = maxDuration // TTL = max session duration\n        \n    case types.CodeInterpreterKind:\n        ci, err := m.agentcubeClient.CodeInterpreters(namespace).Get(\n            ctx, name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n        if err != nil {\n            if apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n                return // use defaults\n            }\n            return ttl, idleTimeout, maxDuration, err\n        }\n        if ci.Spec.SessionTimeout != nil {\n            idleTimeout = ci.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration\n        }\n        if ci.Spec.MaxSessionDuration != nil {\n            maxDuration = ci.Spec.MaxSessionDuration.Duration\n        }\n        ttl = maxDuration\n    }\n\n    return ttl, idleTimeout, maxDuration, nil\n}\n```\n\n### Check Expiration\n\n```go\nfunc (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) IsExpired(sandbox *types.SandboxInfo) bool {\n    return time.Now().After(sandbox.ExpiresAt)\n}\n\nfunc (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) IsIdleExpired(sandbox *types.SandboxInfo, idleTimeout time.Duration) bool {\n    if sandbox.LastActivity.IsZero() {\n        return false\n    }\n    return time.Now().After(sandbox.LastActivity.Add(idleTimeout))\n}\n```\n\n### Garbage Collection Algorithm\n\n```go\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) runOnce(ctx context.Context) error {\n    ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, gc.onceTimeout)\n    defer cancel()\n\n    now := time.Now()\n\n    // 1. List expired sandboxes (TTL reached)\n    expired, err := gc.manager.store.ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, now, 16)\n    if err != nil {\n        return fmt.Errorf(\"list expired: %w\", err)\n    }\n\n    // 2. List inactive sandboxes (idle timeout reached)\n    inactiveBefore := now.Add(-gc.manager.config.DefaultIdleTimeout)\n    inactive, err := gc.manager.store.ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, inactiveBefore, 16)\n    if err != nil {\n        return fmt.Errorf(\"list inactive: %w\", err)\n    }\n\n    // 3. Delete each sandbox\n    allSandboxes := append(expired, inactive...)\n    for _, sb := range allSandboxes {\n        if err := gc.manager.DeleteSandbox(ctx, sb.SessionID); err != nil {\n            gc.manager.logger.Error(\"gc delete failed\",\n                \"sessionID\", sb.SessionID, \"err\", err)\n            continue\n        }\n        gc.manager.logger.Info(\"gc deleted sandbox\",\n            \"sessionID\", sb.SessionID,\n            \"reason\", determineReason(sb, now, inactiveBefore))\n    }\n\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Error Types\n\n| Error | HTTP Status | Code |\n|-------|-------------|------|\n| Session not found | 404 | `NOT_FOUND` |\n| Sandbox CR already deleted | 200 (success) | `deleted` |\n| K8s API error | 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` |\n| Store error | 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` |\n| Timeout during deletion | 503 | `SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE` |\n\n### Graceful Deletion Handling\n\n```go\nfunc handleDeleteError(err error) error {\n    if apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n        // Already deleted - treat as success\n        return nil\n    }\n    if apierrors.IsConflict(err) {\n        // Retry with force delete\n        return &ConflictError{Resource: \"sandbox\", Err: err}\n    }\n    return &InternalError{Err: err}\n}\n```\n\n### Force Delete (Last Resort)\n\n```go\nfunc (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) ForceDeleteSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error {\n    sandboxInfo, err := m.store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n    if err != nil {\n        return err\n    }\n\n    deleteOpts := metav1.DeleteOptions{\n        GracePeriodSeconds: ptr.To[int64](0),\n    }\n\n    // Use foreground deletion finalizer override\n    m.k8sClient.DynamicClient().Resource(sandboxGVR).\n        Namespace(sandboxInfo.SandboxNamespace).\n        Delete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, deleteOpts)\n\n    return m.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n}\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test | Coverage |\n|------|----------|\n| `TestDeleteSandbox` | 正常删除流程、NotFound 处理、K8s 错误处理 |\n| `TestCalculateLifecycle` | 从 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 获取 timeout 配置 |\n| `TestIsExpired` | TTL 过期判断逻辑 |\n| `TestIsIdleExpired` | Idle timeout 过期判断逻辑 |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_runOnce` | GC 单次运行逻辑 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Test | Coverage |\n|------|----------|\n| `TestDeleteSandboxIntegration` | 在 test env 中创建 Sandbox CR 并删除 |\n| `TestGarbageCollectorIntegration` | 启动 GC goroutine，验证定期清理 |\n\n### Mock/Fake Clients\n\n```go\ntype MockStore struct {\n    sandboxes map[string]*types.SandboxInfo\n}\n\ntype MockAgentCubeClient struct {\n    agentRuntimes    map[string]*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime\n    codeInterpreters map[string]*v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter\n}\n\n// Use client-go fake clientset\nfunc NewFakeAgentCubeClient() *AgentCubeClient {\n    clientset := agentcubeclient.NewSimpleClientset()\n    return &AgentCubeClient{clientset: clientset}\n}\n```\n\n### Test File Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── lifecycle_test.go         — LifecycleManager 单元测试\n├── garbage_collector_test.go — GarbageCollector 单元测试\n├── deletion_handler_test.go  — HTTP handler 测试\n├── integration_test.go       — 使用 fake client + mock store 的集成测试\n```\n\n## Validation Checklist\n\n- [ ] 删除 Sandbox CR 时同步清理 store 中的记录\n- [ ] NotFound 错误不阻塞删除流程（视为已删除）\n- [ ] GC 定期清理 expired + inactive sandboxes\n- [ ] 删除操作有 timeout 保护\n- [ ] Force delete 作为 fallback 机制\n- [ ] 与 agentd idle cleanup 不冲突（agentd watch Sandbox CR，workload manager 删除 store 记录）\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- [已解决] GC interval: `2 * time.Minute` (参考 defaults.go)\n- [已解决] GC batch size: 16 (参考 sandbox-orchestration design)\n- [已解决] Deletion timeout: `30s` (参考 defaults.go `SandboxDeleteTimeout`)\n- 是否需要 deletion finalizer 处理？\n- 是否需要支持 graceful shutdown period（GracePeriodSeconds > 0）？\n\n## References\n\n- client-go spec: `.sdd_prompt.md` (deployment/client-go.md)\n- Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/workloadmanager/`\n- sandbox-orchestration design: `sandbox-orchestration/design.md`\n- idle-cleanup design: `idle-cleanup/design.md`\n- shared_types.go: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` (Labels/Annotations constants)\n- defaults.go: `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` (Timeout constants)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/informers_test.go\">\nERROR [78:2] expected declaration, found informers\n</diagnostics>","met